    "name": "心动厨房",
    "steam_appid": 3079770,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到灵界！你可能不记得自己是如何来到这里的，但无须担心，外表可爱、脾气暴躁的鸡灵艾伦会帮你制定计划！在此从农场到餐桌烹饪游戏中，帮助艾伦修缮一家破败的日式餐馆，为客人提供美味菜肴，种植新鲜庄稼并准备特殊食材来满足所有顾客的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras/072da31817e6ce0343342a1d5357520e.avif?t=1771737910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras_big/072da31817e6ce0343342a1d5357520e.avif?t=1771737910 width=800 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经营餐馆：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>制定每日菜单</strong>。尝试不同的新食谱，迎合客户的口味和需求！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心平衡每道菜的<strong>品质</strong>和<strong>烹饪时间</strong>，确保客人满意并<strong>赚取收入</strong>以进行生机！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提前准备外卖餐点</strong>以满足赶时间的客人的需求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras/f8c2370e76ed7404c678fdaf48b5274d.avif?t=1771737910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras_big/f8c2370e76ed7404c678fdaf48b5274d.avif?t=1771737910 width=800 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>农场到餐桌烹饪：</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在小花园中为作物<strong>浇水</strong>并在其成熟后<strong>收获</strong>！使用这些食材为你灵界的朋友们烹饪最新鲜的美味佳肴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细心呵护你的<strong>奶牛</strong>和<strong>母鸡</strong>，确保每天都有新鲜的牛奶喝鸡蛋！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩<strong>小游戏</strong>以准备食谱所需的特定食材：发酵大豆以制作酱油；晒干绿茶叶制成抹茶粉，还有更多趣味小游戏等你发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras/058b4897366524d352c4684ab32ea5cf.avif?t=1771737910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras_big/058b4897366524d352c4684ab32ea5cf.avif?t=1771737910 width=800 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>购买物品与升级：</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细<strong>管理餐馆的财务</strong>，确保有足够的资金为餐馆及自己购买物品。为农场购买新植物；为卧室购买新装饰，还有更多精彩内容！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花费点数以<strong>购买升级</strong>并修缮餐馆，为厨房增添更多工作站，解锁其他内容，让管理餐馆变得更加轻松！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras/18baf9252b8dff5b3a2d52bd850c9895.avif?t=1771737910\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079770/extras_big/18baf9252b8dff5b3a2d52bd850c9895.avif?t=1771737910 width=800 height=317 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索故事剧情：</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这间餐馆一直少了点什么东西。了解<strong>艾伦与餐馆的过去</strong>，帮助他找到遗失的那部分！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾伦说餐馆过去有几位<strong>常客</strong>，当后者光顾时，完成他们的<strong>挑战</strong>以了解餐馆的历史！</p></li></ul>",
